---
title: Fajita Style Whirlpool Spaghetti with Bell Pepper, Onion and Cheese
description: Swirl up the flavours of this water-inspired fajita-style spaghetti into tasty whirlpools!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W28_UK_F14707-2_Main__24low-ef79b893.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/645a6633b0a4d655ddff9b9d.pdf
